      "description": "In this test, the purpose is to record the best 5-sec power. The warm-up consists of low intensity followed by some threshold toggles, then two priming efforts, then 5 sprint attempts. Do at least 2-3 to make sure a good effort was recorded. Although the sprints are programed as 15-sec free ride efforts, you don't need to sprint for the full duration (just go a little beyond 5 sec).\n\n- 8m 30-55%\n- 30s 95-105%\n- 30s 45-55%\n- 30s 95-105%\n- 30s 45-55%\n- 30s 95-105%\n- 30s 45-55%\n- 30s 95-105%\n- 1m 30-55%\n- 1m 30-55%\n- 15s 200-250%\n- 1m 30-55%\n- 10s 260-280%\n- 4m 30-55%\n- 15s Freeride 380-500% - mean max power\n- 3m 20-45%\n- 15s Freeride 380-500% - mean max power\n- 3m 20-45%\n- 15s Freeride 380-500% - mean max power\n- 3m 20-45%\n- 15s Freeride 380-500% - mean max power\n- 3m 20-45%\n- 15s Freeride 380-500% - mean max power\n- 3m 20-45%\n- 8m 30-55%"
